name: Moonweave Gossamer
description: Columbinaâ€™s outfit is a weightless, graceful raiment crafted by the Kuuhenki from Frostmoon Scion fabrics and threaded with strands of gentle moonlight. The Frostmoon Scions, not quite fully understanding what they were seeing, naturally assumed this new vestment to be yet another miracle from Kuutar. No wonder that, ever since then, Columbina would occasionally hear wishes like, "Lady Kuutar, kindly grant me a hand as nimble as your own, I beseech you."
